The solution was :
edit the web.xml

and add to the jsp servlet:

    &lt;init-param&gt;
            &lt;param-name&gt;compilerSourceVM&lt;/param-name&gt;
            &lt;param-value&gt;1.8&lt;/param-value&gt;
        &lt;/init-param&gt;
        &lt;init-param&gt;
