The above abnormality is caused mainly because the server ip and port requested by the client socket have not opened the listening thread. The investigation directions mainly include the following:
1：It may be that the server listening thread corresponding to the ip and port has not been successfully started or has crashed;
2：The server ip or port of the client socket connection is wrong;
3：The client socket connects using a DNS name that resolves to the wrong IP;
It may be blocked by the firewall on the server side, but this possibility is relatively low

